      "title": "Checkout retry policy",
      "space": { "key": "ENG" },
      "body": {
        "view": {
          "value": "<h2>Intended behavior</h2><p>The checkout service retries a failed payment authorization <strong>three</strong> times with exponential backoff.</p><p>A fourth failure is surfaced to the user as <code>PAYMENT_UNAVAILABLE</code>. This is intentional; see the 2025 incident review.</p><script>console.log('nope')</script>"
        }
